## Getting started with your project

### Usage
If you have `uv` then just run
```bash
uv run {{ project_slug }}/main.py
```

#### Virtual environment
If you want to deploy venv first just run
```bash
uv sync && source .venv/bin/activate
```
If you don't have `uv`
```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install {{project_slug}}
```

